      "example_satisfying_only_this_reading": "I strongly urge you to reconsider this path, as it leads only to violence and destruction for yourself and others. It is important to step back and look at how these groups exploit people's frustrations for harmful ends."
    }
  ],
  "ambiguous_phrases": [
